summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Seattle Steel Company, Pacific Coast Steel Company, E. M. Wilson, D. E. McLaughlin and wife, Clara L. McLaughlin, and W. S. Burt and wife, Mary A. Burt, to the City of Seattle, executed on September 10, 1912, for certain portions of Section Thirteen (13), Township Twenty-four (240, North, Range Three (3), East Willamette Meridian, and extending Avalon Way across said tracts.
